03:57.757 --> 04:00.715
What exactly can I do for you?

04:04.300 --> 04:05.755
From what I learned, you were

04:05.757 --> 04:07.965
the one who reported
Klara missing.

04:09.090 --> 04:12.463
And you said that
you had nothing to do

04:12.465 --> 04:15.048
